{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/sort-stability","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","demoType":null,"title":"Utulivu wa kupanga","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kada sortiraš zapise u tabeli po određenoj koloni ili polju, stabilno sortiranje (stable sort) uvek čuva redosled zapisa koji imaju isti ključ.</p>\n<p>Na primer, u ovoj tabeli sa državama i gradovima, stabilno sortiranje po drugoj koloni, gradu, će zadržati Birmingham iz Amerike iznad Birminghama iz Engleske. (Iako nasumično sortiranje <em>može</em>, u ovom slučaju, postavljanje Birminghama iz Amerike iznad Birminghama iz Engleske, stabilan algoritam sortiranja to garantuje).</p>\n<pre>UK  London\nUS  New York\nUS  Birmingham\nUK  Birmingham\n</pre>\n<p>Isto tako, stabilno sortiranje samo po prvoj koloni daće \"UK London\" kao prvi element i \"US Birmingham\" kao poslednji (zato što će redosled elemenata sa istom prvom rečju – \"UK\" ili \"US\" – ostati nepromenjen).</p>\n</section>","id":"5a23c84252665b21eecc8014","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Napišite funkciju koja prima niz podataka sa dve dimenzije kao parametar. Svaki element ima dva sastava, kao što je prikazano u gornjem primeru. Funkcija treba da sortira niz podataka kako je prethodno opisano i vrati sortirani niz.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Rosetta","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302308,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/sort-stability"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function stableSort(arr) {\n\n}","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>stableSort</code> treba da bude funkcija.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof stableSort == 'function');"},{"text":"<p><code>stableSort([[\"UK\", \"London\"], [\"US\", \"New York\"], [\"US\", \"Birmingham\"], [\"UK\", \"Birmingham\"]])</code> Trebalo bi da vrati red podataka.</p>","testString":"assert(\n  Array.isArray(\n    stableSort([\n      ['UK', 'London'],\n      ['US', 'New York'],\n      ['US', 'Birmingham'],\n      ['UK', 'Birmingham']\n    ])\n  )\n);"},{"text":"<p><code>stableSort([[\"UK\", \"London\"], [\"US\", \"New York\"], [\"US\", \"Birmingham\"], [\"UK\", \"Birmingham\"]])</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>[[\"US\", \"Birmingham\"], [\"UK\", \"Birmingham\"], [\"UK\", \"London\"], [\"US\", \"New York\"]]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(\n  stableSort([\n    ['UK', 'London'],\n    ['US', 'New York'],\n    ['US', 'Birmingham'],\n    ['UK', 'Birmingham']\n  ]),\n  [\n    ['US', 'Birmingham'],\n    ['UK', 'Birmingham'],\n    ['UK', 'London'],\n    ['US', 'New York']\n  ]\n);"},{"text":"<p><code>stableSort([[2, 2], [1, 2], [1, 4], [1, 5]])</code> treba da vrati <code>[[2, 2], [1, 2], [1, 4], [1, 5]]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(\n  stableSort([\n    [2, 2],\n    [1, 2],\n    [1, 4],\n    [1, 5]\n  ]),\n  [\n    [2, 2],\n    [1, 2],\n    [1, 4],\n    [1, 5]\n  ]\n);"},{"text":"<p><code>stableSort([[11, 55], [12, 45], [11, 45], [32, 45]])</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>[[12, 45], [11, 45], [32, 45], [11, 55]]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(\n  stableSort([\n    [11, 55],\n    [12, 45],\n    [11, 45],\n    [32, 45]\n  ]),\n  [\n    [12, 45],\n    [11, 45],\n    [32, 45],\n    [11, 55]\n  ]\n);"},{"text":"<p><code>stableSort([[10, 22], [1, 2], [1, 4], [1, 5], [10, 9]])</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>[[1, 2], [1, 4], [1, 5], [10, 9], [10, 22]]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(\n  stableSort([\n    [10, 22],\n    [1, 2],\n    [1, 4],\n    [1, 5],\n    [10, 9]\n  ]),\n  [\n    [1, 2],\n    [1, 4],\n    [1, 5],\n    [10, 9],\n    [10, 22]\n  ]\n);"},{"text":"<p><code>stableSort([[55, 54], [12, 22], [31, 43], [31, 54], [10, 49]])</code> treba da vrati <code>[[12, 22], [31, 43], [10, 49], [55, 54], [31, 54]]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(\n  stableSort([\n    [55, 54],\n    [12, 22],\n    [31, 43],\n    [31, 54],\n    [10, 49]\n  ]),\n  [\n    [12, 22],\n    [31, 43],\n    [10, 49],\n    [55, 54],\n    [31, 54]\n  ]\n);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/rosetta-code/#rosetta-code-challenges","dashedName":"sort-stability","certification":"rosetta-code","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/sort-using-a-custom-comparator","prevChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/sort-disjoint-sublist","id":"5a23c84252665b21eecc8014","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function ZigZagMatrix(n) {\n  const mtx = [];\n  for (let i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n    mtx[i] = [];\n  }\n\n  let i = 1;\n  let j = 1;\n  for (let e = 0; e < n * n; e++) {\n    mtx[i - 1][j - 1] = e;\n    if ((i + j) % 2 === 0) {\n      // Even stripes\n      if (j < n) j++;\n      else i += 2;\n      if (i > 1) i--;\n    } else {\n      // Odd stripes\n      if (i < n) i++;\n      else j += 2;\n      if (j > 1) j--;\n    }\n  }\n  return mtx;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/sort-stability"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}